{"type":null,"faqId":22422,"title":"如何与选购的蓝牙遥控器配对？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in;}\n.p1{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>靠近华为盒子，再同时按住蓝牙遥控器的OK键和音量+</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=74445\" style=\"width:0.3298611in;height:0.31041667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>8秒后松开。启动配对。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>等待一会，如果能够使用，则配对成功。界面右上角会显示蓝牙遥控器的状态图标。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>配对成功后，下次可直接使用，无需再配对。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":246,"faqType":"遥控","useful":3,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"6302","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Remote","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1428628513000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M330","visitedTimes":85,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"M330,MediaQ M330,华为盒子,蓝牙,遥控,配对","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}